<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>425</hymn_number>
<key>Eb</key>
<lyrics>[V1]
 A hlatpi ram um kha ka theih cang, A sunpar nak hohmanh chim khawh lo,
 Ni nak in a ceumi ram chungah, Bawi Jesuh he zungzal um ka duh.

[C1]
   Khi ram ah (khi ram ah) khi ram ah (khi ram ah) Bawi Jesuh he
   zungzal um ka duh (um ka duh) Khi ram ah (khi ram ah) khi ram ah (khi ram
   ah) Bawi Jesuh he zungzal um ka duh.

[V2]
 Baibal ca chung bia ka theih tikah, Thluachuah van luhnak kong kha ka
 theih, Thabat le rawltam tihal nak kha, Khi ram kan phak tikah a dih lai.

[C2]
   Khi ram ah (khi ram ah) khi ram ah (khi ram ah) Bawi Jesuh he
   zungzal um ka duh (um ka duh) Khi ram ah (khi ram ah) khi ram ah (khi ram
   ah) Bawi Jesuh he zungzal um ka duh.

[V3]
 Vancung khua thatnak hodah chim kho? Phannak ngaih-chiatnak a um ti
 lo, Fahnak, tahnak, mithi ngaihnak le, Thih chin zeihmanh a um ti lai lo.

[C3]
   Khi ram ah (khi ram ah) khi ram ah (khi ram ah) Bawi Jesuh he
   zungzal um ka duh (um ka duh) Khi ram ah (khi ram ah) khi ram ah (khi ram
   ah) Bawi Jesuh he zungzal um ka duh.

[V4]
 Khi ramtha chung i um awk caah, Pathian nih misual kha a forh hna,
 Hohmanh a forhnak an zumh ahcun, Zungzal khi ram chungah an um lai.

[C4]
   Khi ram ah (khi ram ah) khi ram ah (khi ram ah) Bawi Jesuh he
   zungzal um ka duh (um ka duh) Khi ram ah (khi ram ah) khi ram ah (khi ram
   ah) Bawi Jesuh he zungzal um ka duh.</lyrics>
<title>KHI RAM AH UM KA DUH CH425</title>
</song>